    </p>
    <p>5. Emotes, Pets &amp; Items</p>
    <p>
      Please deactivate emote logs.<br />
      Only use weapons or pets if they fit your RP character.
    </p>
    <p>6. Rooms &amp; Usage</p>
    <p>
      Rooms may be used freely.<br />
      If staff requires a room for massages or photos, please vacate it when asked.
    </p>
    <p>8. Enforcement</p>
